Multi Duty Tab New Tab is a modern and easy-to-use tool that delivers a superior customer experience powered by Bing.

Multi Duty Tab is an accessible and user-friendly new tab extension designed specifically to manage your day-to-day needs.
It allows you to set a beautifully simplistic New Tab page that includes search provided by Bing, clock, background filled with different pictures, that is automatically changes once in a while, and an inspiring quote from prominent person to make you feel more productive, to streamline your daily routine.

Multi Duty Tab is the best and most advanced extension to boost your productivity.

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to install "Multi Duty Tab" Chrome extension and hereby agree to set Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service and the Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.

You may remove this extension at any time from the chrome extension page.
